995
01:18:17.943 --> 01:18:20.029
<i>You may remember reading about it.</i>

996
01:18:20.279 --> 01:18:23.365
<i>It made the papers
and got his picture in</i> Look <i>magazine.</i>

997
01:18:23.574 --> 01:18:24.909
