1008
01:18:58.525 --> 01:19:01.570
<i>There are 100 different ways
to skim off the top.</i>

1009
01:19:01.779 --> 01:19:04.281
<i>Men, materials, you name it.</i>

1010
01:19:04.615 --> 01:19:07.493
<i>And oh, my Lord,
how the money rolled in!</i>

1011
01:19:07.701 --> 01:19:10.246
