committed elsewhere.

1021
01:19:55.249 --> 01:19:58.335
You be sure and thank Maisie
for this fine pie.

1022
01:19:59.420 --> 01:20:01.588
<i>And behind every shady deal...</i>

1023
01:20:01.922 --> 01:20:04.550
<i>...behind every dollar earned...</i>

1024
01:20:04.842 --> 01:20:07.886
<i>...there was Andy, keeping the books.</i>

