That's the trade off.

1087
01:24:11.797 --> 01:24:14.424
<i>Tommy Williams
came to Shawshank in 1905...</i>

1088
01:24:14.633 --> 01:24:16.885
<i>...on a two-year stretch for B and E.</i>

1089
01:24:17.135 --> 01:24:19.471
<i>That's breaking and entering to you.</i>

1090
01:24:19.721 --> 01:24:23.976
<i>Cops caught him sneaking TV sets
