1091
01:24:24.393 --> 01:24:25.686
<i>Young punk.</i>

1092
01:24:25.894 --> 01:24:27.521
<i>Mr. Rock 'n' Roll...</i>

1093
01:24:27.729 --> 01:24:29.273
<i>...cocky as hell.</i>

1094
01:24:29.481 --> 01:24:31.858
