let me tell you.

1105
01:25:10.230 --> 01:25:12.190
Weekend furloughs. Work programs.

1106
01:25:12.858 --> 01:25:14.151
Not like here.

1107
01:25:14.318 --> 01:25:16.069
Sounds like you done time all over.

1108
01:25:16.528 --> 01:25:18.905
I've been in and out since I was 13.

1109
01:25:19.114 --> 01:25:21.325
Name it, chances are I've been there.

1110
01:25:21.533 --> 01:25:24.202
