1115
01:25:36.715 --> 01:25:37.716
Me?

1116
01:25:40.135 --> 01:25:41.803
A lawyer fucked me.

1117
01:25:45.724 --> 01:25:48.685
Everybody's innocent in here.
Don't you know that?

1118
01:25:56.568 --> 01:26:00.989
<i>As it turned out, Tommy had himself
a young wife and a new baby girl.</i>

1119
01:26:01.573 --> 01:26:03.700
<i>Maybe he thought of them
on the streets...</i>

1120
01:26:03.909 --> 01:26:06.411
<i>...or his child growing up
not knowing her daddy.</i>

1121
01:26:06.703 --> 01:26:08.080
<i>Whatever it was...</i>

1122
01:26:08.413 --> 01:26:10.832
<i>...something lit a fire
under that boy's ass.</i>

1123
01:26:14.670 --> 01:26:17.547
