1127
01:26:29.476 --> 01:26:31.311
-You mean that?
-Yeah.

1128
01:26:32.979 --> 01:26:34.439
You really mean that?

1129
01:26:35.440 --> 01:26:36.817
Yes, sir, I do.

1130
01:26:37.025 --> 01:26:38.985
