1138
01:27:04.052 --> 01:27:06.179
<i>So Andy took Tommy under his wing.</i>

1139
01:27:06.388 --> 01:27:09.015
<i>Started walking him through his ABC's.</i>

1140
01:27:11.143 --> 01:27:13.353
