1145
01:27:28.326 --> 01:27:30.579
<i>But that wasn't the only reason.</i>

1146
01:27:31.288 --> 01:27:33.498
<i>Prison time is slow time.</i>

1147
01:27:33.957 --> 01:27:36.543
<i>So you do what you can to keep going.</i>

1148
01:27:36.877 --> 01:27:38.962
<i>Some fellas collect stamps.</i>

1149
01:27:39.337 --> 01:27:41.840
<i>Others build matchstick houses.</i>

1150
01:27:42.424 --> 01:27:45.093
<i>Andy built a library.</i>

1151
01:27:45.594 --> 01:27:47.512
<i>Now he needed a new project.</i>

1152
01:27:48.388 --> 01:27:49.890
<i>Tommy was it.</i>

1153
01:27:50.515 --> 01:27:54.519
<i>It was the same reason he spent years
