1154
01:27:55.061 --> 01:27:58.315
<i>The same reason he hung
his fantasy girlies on the wall.</i>

1155
01:27:59.191 --> 01:28:00.484
<i>In prison...</i>

1156
01:28:00.734 --> 01:28:04.488
